        "response": [
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "[{\"ref_id\":0,\"content\":\"Here are the latest sales trends based on recent data:\\n\\n- The ELECTRICAL category is currently showing strong sales, with a sales weight of 1.531 for the year 2026, indicating an upward trend.\\n- Within this category, products such as AFCI Breaker 15-Amp, Armored Cable BX 12-2, GFCI Breaker 20-Amp, LED Flush Mount Ceiling, and Outdoor Extension Cord 50ft are contributing significantly.\\n- There are clear seasonal effects: Sales multipliers tend to peak in October (1.4), November (1.6), and December (1.5), suggesting higher sales during fall and the holiday period. The lowest seasonal multiplier is in March (1.0), indicating somewhat slower sales early in the year.\\n- All products in this category follow a similar seasonal pattern, with sales building up through the year and peaking towards the end of the calendar year.\\n\\nOverall, the latest sales data shows strong performance in electrical products, with especially high demand anticipated during the last quarter of the year.\"}]"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
